Bellum Gens Elite is a premier esports LAN event organized in Bulgaria. Ancient history and traditions, and beautiful scenery combine with high-level action-packed esports competition to bring you an unforgettable experience.

Bellum Gens Elite Balkan weekly online circuit launches in November 2024 and presents every player in the Balkan region with the opportunity to participate in weekly online matches to earn points towards cash prizes.
Open to everyone in the Balkan region
Compete weekly to earn points towards monthly cash prizes
Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora returns in 2025 for another epic showdown!

The Summer Theater in Stara Zagora is located at the foot of largest city park in Bulgaria. This open-air masterpiece combines nature and ancient traditions with modern architecture into a unique experience for the audience.

The city hosting this event has more than 8000 years of history! Ancient forums, Roman murals and mosaics, 2000-year-old theaters, bath houses, and aqueducts, it's all beneath your feet and everywhere around you. Traditions and modern esports come together at this unique place!
Bellum Gens joined forces with the Bulgarian StarCraft League and Stara Zagora Municipality to deliver an epic esports experience!
Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora 2020 brought the top Counter-Strike talent in the region to compete under one roof for a prize pool of $10,000!
Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora was one of the few LAN events held in 2020 and due to Covid-19 lockdowns and travel restrictions, only 10 teams were able to participate in the LAN finals.
Contact us if you wish to sponsor this or any of the other event organized by Bellum Gens. Our social media contacts can be found at the footer of the page.

Bulgarian StarCraft League a one of a kind StarCraft II league in Bulgaria and are contributing to the development of Bulgarian talent in this esport! All StarCraft 2 games in the Esports Business League are casted by the them!
Stara Zagora is a 6000+ year-old city in the center of Bulgaria. We partner with Stara Zagora Municipality for the Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora premier esports event!

Registrations are restricted to participants from the Balkan countries. Registrations have no age restrictions. Registrations for this event are not in any way binding and participation can be halted by the registrant at any point of time. Registrations can also be deleted by the user through the user profile settings menu.

Registrations show intent for participation, but weekly participation would require timely weekly check-ins and being on-time for the matches. All applicants must reside in one of the listed Balkan countries. If an applicant is discovered to permanently reside outside of the listed Balkan countries, that would lead to permanent disqualification from the league and nullification of any points earned.
Provided battle tag, discord ID, should match with the accounts the applicant uses during the League.
Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora 2024 featured the top StarCraft II talent clashing in a 4-day LAN event! Clement "Clem" Desplanches is the champion of Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2024!
Esports Business League is a gaming event for your office! Build better team bonds by friendly or competitive gaming, or get your team to compete against other companies to show how good you are!

Recruit your team and manage your team member roles, team strategies, practice times and more. The only online CS:GO strategy editor freely available to everyone! Discuss public strategies with everyone and build private strategies for your team.

Bellum Gens is a gaming and esports event organizer and consultant focused on the development and popularization of esports in Bulgaria. We want to make esports a recognizable topic for the business and thus to help the development of all esports project in Bulgaria and on the Balkans. If you take interest in esports and want to advertise through esports, position your brand in tournaments, streams, or other gaming and esports channels, then we can help! Contact us for more information on available opportunities.

Bellum Gens is the organizer of the premier Bellum Gen Elite esports event. First held in the town of Stara Zagora, under the name Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora, BGE brought the top Counter-Strike talent in the region to compete under one roof for a prize pool of $10,000! Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2024 features top StarCraft II players from around the world with a prize pool of €10000!

Bellum Gens is the organizer of the Esports Business League - a competitive amateur gaming event for the office. Miltiple companies in Bulgaria participated in seasons one and two of the Esports Business League both for fun and team building and to show which company has the best gamers among their employees!

Bellum Gens offers a CS:GO team finding and team management application, which allows players to look for teams matching their skill and availability, and team owners to manage their teams' roster and general organization. Because CS:GO is a team game!

We are thrilled to announce a 3-year partnership between Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora and TechHub.bg! 🤝

TechHub.bg makes tech shopping both easy and inspiring! With a wide range of high-quality products for home and office, they build a trusted community of enthusiasts and professionals. Your satisfaction is their top priority – discover the difference with TechHub.bg!

Together, we are committed to fostering the growth and development of esports in our region. This collaboration will bring new opportunities, events, and initiatives to support our vibrant gaming community. 🎮✨

🌟We are thrilled to present Visit Stara Zagora as the main official partner of Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora! This partnership marks a significant step forward in enhancing the development of esports in Bulgaria and raising awareness of Stara Zagora as a premier esports destination in the country.🌟

Stara Zagora is a real treasure trove for researchers. Here you can walk around the home of people who lived 8,000 years ago, walk along a fully preserved ancient street of the Roman city of Augusta Trayana, feel the spirit of the Renaissance and embark on many other exploratory missions. The city is extremely convenient for visiting and walking with an organized group.
Together, we aim to create a vibrant esports community and provide unparalleled opportunities for gamers and fans alike. 🎮

🎉We are thrilled to announce that BulStream is the official production partner of Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora! 🏆 BulStream has exclusively secured production for all events hosted by Bellum Gens - Esports Business League and Bellum Gens Elite.

With their world-class production capabilities and exceptional live streaming services, BulStream is dedicated to delivering the highest quality esports experience to all viewers. Get ready for an unparalleled esports journey! 🎮✨
Together, we aim to achieve top-tier production quality and deliver the ultimate esports experience for both players and audiences! 🚀
